{"type": "article", "id": 25328, "title": "Fendi 庆祝 90 周年，以及，Hypebeast 申请 IPO｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-04-12T10:39:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 2443, "name": "杂志"}, {"id": 13253, "name": "估值"}, {"id": 1522, "name": "加州"}, {"id": 117, "name": "纽约"}, {"id": 2862, "name": "旗舰店"}, {"id": 19485, "name": "Hypebeast"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 779, "name": "Prada"}, {"id": 3592, "name": "The North Face"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607132642wuBMV8LFQdcyRKl7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Fendi-to-mark-90th-birthday-with-haute-fourrure-fashion-show,680195.html#.Vww_RoQrJQY\"><b>Fendi 庆祝 90 周年，将举办高定皮草秀</b></a>｜7 月 7 日，意大利奢侈品牌 Fendi 将在罗马举办一场高级定制皮草时装秀（\"haute fourrure\" ），庆祝品牌的 90 周年，而皮革和皮草是 Fendi 最常用到的面料。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Prada-says-shop-closures-to-offset-openings-in-2016-17,680305.html#rc\"><b>Prada 未来开店同时将关闭旧店保持平衡</b></a>｜米兰奢侈品牌 Prada 宣布今明两年将在新开门店的同时关闭一部分旧店，以在疲软的需求中获得一定的利润空间。Prada 的董事长 Carlo Mazzi 周一表示看不到巨大的市场趋势转变，由全球经济情况而造成的市场问题对每个人来说都愈发清晰。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/The-north-face-signs-lease-for-midtown-manhattan-store,680258.html#rc\"><b>The North Face 将在曼哈顿中城开旗舰店</b></a>｜The North Face 本月签下纽约城 2 万平方英尺旗舰店的租约，曼哈顿中城的空间坐落于第五大道 510 号，此前是品牌 Joe Fresh 的店铺。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/bof-exclusive/hypebeast-files-for-ipo\"><b>Hypebeast 申请 IPO</b></a>｜创立于香港的男士潮流生活方式网站 Hypebeast 近日宣布申请 IPO（首次公开募股），这是其成立的第 11 年，目前包含线上杂志 Hypebeast 、线上商店 HBX、女性时尚网站 Popbee 和音乐网站 Hypetrak。发行 5 亿股，股价 0.12-0.14 港币，市值在 2.4 亿港币至 2.8 亿港币之间（约合 3100 万－3600 万美元）。周一收市，Hypebeast 估值达 21 亿港币（约合 2.7 亿美元）。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Lvmh-q1-sales-miss-forecasts-says-france-remains-weak,680217.html#rc\"><b>LVMH 一季度销售额不达预期</b></a>｜奢侈品集团 LVMH 周一发布财报显示一季度销售额低于预期，源于香港、法国等重要市场的游客购物消费下跌。一季度销售额 86.2 亿欧元（约合 98.3 亿美元），低于路透社此前的 87.2 亿欧元的预测值。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/marni-porter-pop-collection\">Marni 与 Porter 合作推出一个包袋系列</a>，价格在 600-730 美元之间：</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132629nChYI2VHZT5lkw0x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">传奇超模吉赛尔·邦辰（Gisele Bundchen）近日为巴西<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/gisele-bundchen-vivara-2016-campaign/\">珠宝品牌 Vivara 拍摄广告</a>：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071326306CqD1yFJTYVoi4gp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132631XI84NFzJAj7Ylktg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.795\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132631okO37KxFtNCAEafB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68240741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">而正当红的超模 Kate Bock 则为 <i>Woman Spain </i>拍摄了一组四月刊的大片，主题为<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/kate-bock-loungewear-woman-spain/\">“The Mexican Dream”</a>：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071326321tUYKnquvTB3gbD0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132632qr3fLCDKxjhBoE1A.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132633Ho2VF3Zc8RwhEzku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132633urg3YTCcaAlPEsL2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132634YSOhnPaCBoT3kJF1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132634B5tz1UZEeuc7wL8a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.32625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">韩国美妆品牌爱丽小屋（韩国美妆品牌 Etude House）推出樱花系列（Pink Cherry Blossom），包括彩妆笔、喷雾、化妆包等等：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132635AaPN5c7W90CzQHKh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132635ZzmRADU1TY3kBdyS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132636qhYzmCuMng7aZVc4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">COS 在米兰家居展上带来了由日本建筑师 Sou Fujimoto 设计的艺术装置：<a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/cos-forest-of-light-installation\">光之丛林（Forest of Light）</a></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132636r6up5NVjdiIhUteH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132637zeo69Is43TMafRkN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132637ChTYPLUFSMlvc9mD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132638CTRPBsbpZFX9Jh5v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132638jwSXhoUateiqy8KF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">Armani 旗下休闲副线 Armani Exchange 在阳光充沛的加州马里布拍摄了<a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/armani-exchange-spring-2016-campaign/\">春夏大片</a>：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132639FOoMTABZCuc2pzgh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071326396TZVNomQlJgq5XCr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071326399Eh1m7sfdK0S25qC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132640ChaD9q0AslBpRydM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607132641VWo174bNZOmdIRHw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071326418QGaHCdUzvV3F1Lr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}